# 🤖 Health Assistant Chatbot (WhatsApp & SMS)

An AI-powered healthcare chatbot designed to provide instant medical guidance through **WhatsApp and SMS**, making healthcare assistance accessible even without internet-based applications.

---

## 🚀 Overview

This chatbot allows users to describe their symptoms and receive guidance on:

* Possible health conditions
* Immediate actions to take
* Safety precautions

---

## 💡 Features

### 📱 Multi-Platform Support

* WhatsApp integration
* SMS support for low-internet users

---

### 🧠 AI-Based Health Guidance

* Understands user input using NLP
* Provides smart and relevant responses
* Suggests precautions and next steps

---

### ⚡ Fast & Accessible

* No need to install apps
* Works directly through messaging

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### ⚙️ Backend

* Node.js / Express.js

### 🤖 AI / NLP

* Natural Language Processing (NLP)
* Machine Learning models

### 📡 Communication APIs

* WhatsApp Business API (or Twilio API)
* SMS Gateway (Twilio / Fast2SMS)

### 🔥 Database

* Firebase / Firestore

### ☁️ Deployment

* Cloud Functions / Firebase Hosting / Server Deployment

---

## 🎯 Purpose

To provide quick, reliable, and accessible healthcare assistance anytime, anywhere.

---

## ⚠️ Disclaimer

This chatbot provides general guidance and should not replace professional medical advice.

